The paper focuses on integrating machine learning with relational database management systems (RDBMS) for efficient model storage and inference. This topic falls under the intersection of database systems (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), with potential implications for distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE) as well.
